WEBVTT

00:01.030 --> 00:02.489
That feels good, doesn't it?

00:02.771 --> 00:03.840
Doesn't it, honey?

00:04.231 --> 00:05.819
I got a great meal for you.

00:06.633 --> 00:07.633
Yes, I do.

00:08.440 --> 00:09.440
Yes, I do.

00:10.047 --> 00:11.333
That's a good girl.

00:11.996 --> 00:14.493
Now you finish up all those vegetables.

00:14.831 --> 00:17.414
I mixed it up for you
just the way you like it.

00:17.484 --> 00:18.555
Yes, I did.

00:19.956 --> 00:20.956
Yes, I do.

00:21.413 --> 00:22.413
Yes, I do.

00:22.560 --> 00:24.417
You're the prettiest baby on this farm.

00:24.418 --> 00:25.418
Yes, you are.

00:25.911 --> 00:26.911
Yes, you are.

00:27.464 --> 00:28.464
Harvey.

00:31.017 --> 00:32.017
Hello, James.

00:32.275 --> 00:33.686
I figured you'd be here.

00:34.927 --> 00:37.255
I heard she took
another blue ribbon on Sunday.

00:37.331 --> 00:40.625
That's right-- we're going
to Sacramento in three weeks.

00:40.733 --> 00:43.392
Now why don't you two just get
married already and make it legal?

00:43.393 --> 00:45.445
What the hell you talking about?
She's a pig.

00:45.452 --> 00:46.622
Harvey, it's a joke.

00:46.642 --> 00:47.936
Well, it wasn't funny.

00:48.498 --> 00:50.003
I was just down in the gulch.

00:50.116 --> 00:52.124
It's all still there, James.
I'm no fool.

00:52.456 --> 00:54.085
You said you'd get rid of it by Friday.

00:54.121 --> 00:56.423
Relax--
we've been neighbors, what, 15 years?

00:56.424 --> 00:58.317
- Right.
- You're a businessman, right?

00:58.318 --> 00:59.318
Right.

01:01.175 --> 01:02.175
$10,000.

01:02.727 --> 01:03.926
And I know you could use it.

01:03.990 --> 01:06.198
This isn't about the money.
It's about the law.

01:06.386 --> 01:08.299
All right, I got it.
You're a Boy Scout.

01:10.588 --> 01:11.588
15 grand.

01:13.041 --> 01:15.510
That'll buy you
a whole lot of merit badges

01:15.511 --> 01:17.891
and a pretty pink bonnet
for your girlfriend too.

01:18.858 --> 01:21.452
You keep that money, 'cause
you're gonna need it for a lawyer.

01:21.523 --> 01:23.284
I'm calling Sheriff Butterfield.

01:25.049 --> 01:26.049
Harvey, wait.

01:27.301 --> 01:28.301
Okay, you win.

01:29.111 --> 01:30.111
I'll do it.

01:30.514 --> 01:33.119
I will do it.
I promise I'll get rid of it.

01:34.917 --> 01:35.917
I promise.

01:36.668 --> 01:37.917
But I can't do it tonight.

01:38.030 --> 01:39.333
Now, I need 24 hours.

01:40.125 --> 01:41.477
That's all I'm asking--

01:41.523 --> 01:44.313
one day,
and it'll all be gone, guaranteed.

01:45.928 --> 01:46.928
Okay.

01:46.935 --> 01:47.935
24 hours.

01:48.086 --> 01:49.144
Thank you, Harvey.

01:49.684 --> 01:50.684
Good man.

01:50.783 --> 01:51.783
Good pig too.

